Drizzona is a comune (municipality) in the Province of Cremona in the Italian region Lombardy, located about 100km southeast of Milan and about 25km east of Cremona. Drizzona borders the following municipalities: Canneto sull'Oglio, Isola Dovarese, Piadena, Torre de' Picenardi, Voltido.  
